OL,3,CResurfaced roads to be relaid again
OL,4,Cafter fault in tarmac
OL,6,FSome roads in Guernsey will need to be
OL,7,Fresurfaced again due to a fault in the
OL,8,Ftarmac that was used.
OL,10,FRonez Construction is the sole
OL,11,Fsupplier of asphalt in the island,
OL,12,Fproducing around 13,000 tonnes of the
OL,13,Fcomposite material each year.
OL,15,FHowever, in spring 2025, the company
OL,16,Fdiscovered an issue in around 200
OL,17,Ftonnes of its supply.
