OL,3,CResurfaced roads to be relaid again
OL,4,Cafter fault in tarmac
OL,6,FThe issue arose soon after Ronez moved
OL,7,Fits quarrying operations to a new site
OL,8,Fat Chouet in late 2024.
OL,10,FThe different geology meant that early
OL,11,Fstone supplies were contaminated with
OL,12,Fclay, which is now contributing to
OL,13,Froad surface failures.
OL,15,FAlthough clay is usually removed
OL,16,Fduring processing, prolonged wet
OL,17,Fweather last year caused some to stick
OL,18,Fto the stone and enter the mix.
