OL,3,CResurfaced roads to be relaid again
OL,4,Cafter fault in tarmac
OL,6,FWhile the construction company is
OL,7,Fpaying to fix the issues, motorists
OL,8,Fface more road closures and disruption
OL,9,Fas the problem is sorted out.
OL,11,FGary Reynolds, a taxi driver in
OL,12,FGuernsey, said: "A lot of the time we
OL,13,Fhear from clients that they're fed up
OL,14,Fwith coming over, they're not going to
OL,15,Fspend the money to come here because
OL,16,Fof the problems with getting in and
OL,17,Fout."
