OL,3,CResurfaced roads to be relaid again
OL,4,Cafter fault in tarmac
OL,6,FA statement from Guernsey's Traffic
OL,7,Fand Highway Services reads: "An issue
OL,8,Fwith the asphalt supplied for
OL,9,Fresurfacing projects was first
OL,10,Fidentified towards the end of 2024.
OL,12,F"We are continuing to monitor
OL,13,Fresurfaced roads and are working
OL,14,Fclosely with Ronez to identify any
OL,15,Fother areas requiring rectification
OL,16,Funder guarantee."
